{"tid":1039927,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S10 超聲波   又贏~~~~","createTime":"2019-02-27T17:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T02:06:19.000Z","uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51c163d425855b4512d2f456f980a2a5f2fb7364","tid":1039927,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/faUEM-szlnY?t=278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfaUEM-szlnY%3Ft%3D278&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=532c92d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/faUEM-szlnY?t=278</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4e3dc7d0851f3028c77a11e5dd3f75970d94ee","tid":1039927,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eDvttvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeDvttvR.jpg&h=ce60c0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPvEAaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPvEAaS.jpg&h=898067a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bacd1fa8e81f28fd44dda8784338b25e04866fb","tid":1039927,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2011/03/19/internet-gunner/headline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2011%2F03%2F19%2Finternet-gunner%2Fheadline%2F&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=20bee5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2011/03/19/internet-gunner/headline/</a><br />\n<br />\n在網絡資訊爆炸的年代，「打手」隨處可見。由於網絡打手是屬於「黑暗」層面的工作，公司絕不會光明正大的登報聘請，一般都是以其他職位來掩飾。如今竟有公司明目張膽地在 JIJIS 騁請網絡打手，令人覺得網絡打手真的無處不在，以下我們請來網絡打手「阿偉」作訪問，爆一些他們行內鮮為人知的內幕工作..<br />\n<br />\n好多廠商都評批打手收費昂費，你們有那些看法?<br />\n<br />\n其實現時巿場上打手價格很參差，由幾百到幾十萬都有，以上提到樓主那些劣等打手一般收費很便宜，因為都是一些「黃毛丫頭」以為網上發發言就可以成為打手，公司貪便宜聘用這些沒經驗的打手，最後得不到宣傳效用又令自己品牌受損。我知道還有很多公司為了節省金錢，命其下員工自行操刀，最後當然是失敗收場。收費昂貴的原因當然是有我們的秘密武器，一般打手的戰場是香港知名的討論區，化妝品的有 <a href=\"http://she.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshe.com&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=7d4b6648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">she.com</a> 及 beauty exchange ,飲食有 openrice,電腦有 hkepc，親子有 baby kingom，其他有 uwants,discuss 及 hkgolden。這些網站收一則 banner 廣告以數萬元至數十萬元作單位，我們打手還要每天派多人特地去「推 POST」及護航，是一項有組織系統、花時間、人力及智慧的工作，試問怎可能收費便宜呢?"},{"pid":"0f7e6e2819cced96d13177b7bc681aa3c3bce8bb","tid":1039927,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}